collectors.title: Database
collectors.titleDetails: (40 total Queries, 40 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT `appointment`.`appointmentDate`, (SELECT SUM(appointmentFee) FROM appointment a WHERE a.appointmentDate = appointment.appointmentDate) as totalRevenue, COUNT(appointment.appointmentID) as totalAppointments FROM `appointment` WHERE `appointment`.`businessID` = '39' AND `appointment`.`appointmentDate` >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 7 DAY) GROUP BY `appointment`.`appointmentDate`

SELECT DATE_FORMAT(Date, '%Y-%m-%d') as label, SUM(Value) as total FROM `invoices` WHERE `idBusiness` = '39' AND WEEKDAY(Date) >= 0 AND WEEKDAY(Date) <= 6 AND YEARWEEK(Date, 1) = YEARWEEK(CURDATE(), 1) GROUP BY `label` ORDER BY `Date`

SELECT CONCAT(MONTH(createdAT), '-', YEAR(createdAT)) AS label, SUM(hospitalCharges) AS hospitalCharges FROM appointment WHERE businessID = '39' GROUP BY YEAR(createdAT), MONTH(createdAT) ORDER BY YEAR(createdAT), MONTH(createdAT)

SELECT CONCAT(MONTH(Date), '-', YEAR(Date)) AS label, COALESCE(SUM(Value), 0) AS hospitalCharges FROM invoices WHERE idBusiness = '39' GROUP BY YEAR(Date), MONTH(Date) ORDER BY YEAR(Date), MONTH(Date)

SELECT CONCAT(MONTH(createdAT), '-', YEAR(createdAT)) AS label, SUM(hospitalCharges) AS totalCharges FROM labtest WHERE businessId = '39' GROUP BY YEAR(CreatedAT), MONTH(CreatedAT) ORDER BY YEAR(CreatedAT), MONTH(CreatedAT)

SELECT MONTH(appointmentDate) as month, SUM(appointmentFee) as total FROM `generalopd` WHERE `businessID` = '39' AND YEAR(appointmentDate) = '2024' AND `status` = 'completed' AND `isFreeCamp` = 0 GROUP BY MONTH(appointmentDate) ORDER BY MONTH(appointmentDate) ASC

SELECT MONTH(Date) as month, SUM(Value) as total FROM `invoices` WHERE `idBusiness` = '39' AND YEAR(Date) = '2024' AND `Status` = 'closed' AND `isSummaryInvoice` = 0 GROUP BY MONTH(Date) ORDER BY MONTH(Date) ASC
SELECT MONTH(CreatedAT) as month, SUM(fee) as total FROM `labtest` WHERE `businessId` = '39' AND YEAR(CreatedAT) = '2024' GROUP BY MONTH(CreatedAT) ORDER BY MONTH(CreatedAT) ASC

SELECT MONTH(appointmentDate) as month, SUM(appointmentFee + hospitalCharges) as total FROM `appointment` WHERE `businessID` = '39' AND YEAR(appointmentDate) = '2024' GROUP BY MONTH(appointmentDate) ORDER BY MONTH(appointmentDate) ASC
